{"tid":479101,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"十年可唔可能學識一個陌生語言？","createTime":"2017-11-24T17:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T05:52:32.000Z","uid":103953,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"efaae49f8fed6803d64cb94c3af9ed1852fee8c7","tid":479101,"uid":103953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:17:29.000Z","msg":"情境：假設有一個十歲嘅細路被安排喺一個非母語語系嘅國家生活，佢唯一嘅生活限制係唔能夠接受任何有關學習該語言嘅課程（就計老豆老母都唔能夠教佢），只可以靠自己平時日常生活、睇電視、睇書、聽收音機等等去接觸果個語言，有冇可能可以用十年時間學識果個語文呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n（條件：可以做到基本對話及讀寫）"},{"pid":"4ef43429728e85edc39ac7b521a8da805d9a7c6e","tid":479101,"uid":46933,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"2年都夠有突"},{"pid":"5f201931cc445be47cd3910e87c3cd85d4248166","tid":479101,"uid":128119,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:25:34.000Z","msg":"一年都夠做"},{"pid":"b81e833e4c8ae883d92b60acaa23748995ffef1e","tid":479101,"uid":41243,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:27:38.000Z","msg":"on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十年? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe26463963b9fc973edded35922b849ab1cddf2a","tid":479101,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:33:16.000Z","msg":"小朋友5年內得"},{"pid":"0ff88d853222b35b99d7d8848e91301a876eaff8","tid":479101,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:34:08.000Z","msg":"你個情境設定都有問題啦<br />\n佢十歲唔洗返學嘅咩<br />\n學校一定教佢哋官方嘅語言"},{"pid":"69570e4d83ffe47f593a68fab1cd001a75068fb6","tid":479101,"uid":103953,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:39:29.000Z","msg":"我係咁諗，<br />\n一個人如果唔係細細個就俾老豆老母教一啲簡單嘅生字，例如：肚餓、口渴、眼訓等等......<br />\n真係分分鐘要好耐先意會到呢啲字係點解，仲要如果貿貿然去左個陌生嘅國家又冇人教你，就算咁叻俾你學識聽同埋表達，都唔係咁易可以書寫到出黎，如果唔係大陸都唔會有咁多文盲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc2efab0e4078f83bdc7bd52f570573d8bbf2e0","tid":479101,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:40:58.000Z","msg":"三至五歲起步嘅話 八歲前都學到好流利啦<br />\n利申：大學讀過一個linguistic course"},{"pid":"1090baf7187052288f43ec240b288eb8f4cb31cd","tid":479101,"uid":103953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三至五歲起步嘅話 八歲前都學到好流利啦<br />\n利申：大學讀過一個linguistic course</blockquote><br />\n如果錯過左黃金學習期呢？"},{"pid":"26f3ea95e46cf6d36baf24d5db763610160ada41","tid":479101,"uid":25699,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:42:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係咁諗，<br />\n一個人如果唔係細細個就俾老豆老母教一啲簡單嘅生字，例如：肚餓、口渴、眼訓等等......<br />\n真係分分鐘要好耐先意會到呢啲字係點解，仲要如果貿貿然去左個陌生嘅國家又冇人教你，就算咁叻俾你學識聽同埋表達，都唔係咁易可以書寫到出黎，如果唔係大陸都唔會有咁多文盲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n文盲係唔識寫字 唔係唔識語言"},{"pid":"a314efee7b4d013a773251fc042feb2eb7b4d07c","tid":479101,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:42:46.000Z","msg":"點解唔得先 你答返我"},{"pid":"fcf6e721c81d3adaed2664d25f01ef9841ea474d","tid":479101,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:43:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f943e6379521c8aaeaf1f8542ed005725f37572e","tid":479101,"uid":51978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三至五歲起步嘅話 八歲前都學到好流利啦<br />\n利申：大學讀過一個linguistic course</blockquote><br />\n不過回應返樓主嘅假設 十歲起步嘅話 唔上正規課程 只靠自學<br />\n我諗六至十年都夠佢同人暢通順利溝通 不過應該會有語法錯誤／不地道口音 即係好難精通 利申9up"},{"pid":"00d05291a8cecf8cd77d5a67861631bb60d42109","tid":479101,"uid":152376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:44:06.000Z","msg":"我覺得有難度 因為如果無任何人教你之下 係好難去理解當中嘅意思 就算生字記到 文法同講嘢方面都比較難認識"},{"pid":"af7d3c2a28f2abc1d52de52c438b77aad7d90377","tid":479101,"uid":39889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:48:02.000Z","msg":"屋企請過工人既<br />\n就知要學其實可以好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中文已經算難學<br />\n但基本上一年左右都可以做到9成日常生活對答"},{"pid":"1fbc564b2b0a02b7d21f4963ca4ac9e957479012","tid":479101,"uid":103953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企請過工人既<br />\n就知要學其實可以好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中文已經算難學<br />\n但基本上一年左右都可以做到9成日常生活對答</blockquote><br />\n同意要聽同講應該唔洗好耐，但要掌握到書寫呢部分，冇返三五七年都應該好難做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fd2a6c2c1040745ac8298c4410e2fe8f84afe8","tid":479101,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企請過工人既<br />\n就知要學其實可以好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中文已經算難學<br />\n但基本上一年左右都可以做到9成日常生活對答</blockquote><br />\n但係唔睇樣你都聽得出佢唔係本地人"},{"pid":"a5c83af759e6b8e105c770c96715c924a5b0fd39","tid":479101,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:54:09.000Z","msg":"如果20歲開始得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86667244438fcf5fed928e5a90d8ba44349ece3","tid":479101,"uid":135390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:54:19.000Z","msg":"身體語言表達頭幾次<br />\n有人同佢講多幾次就會記得<br />\n記得之後會自己試下跟住人地講<br />\n之後再改正發音<br />\n最後識埋"},{"pid":"151243858a157a366306c00411f856eb4a435580","tid":479101,"uid":128150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個情境設定都有問題啦<br />\n佢十歲唔洗返學嘅咩<br />\n學校一定教佢哋官方嘅語言</blockquote><br />\n你唔明乜野叫設題？返小學學下先"},{"pid":"e0e1b96925b04266e57b13710a4537900701c74c","tid":479101,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:58:00.000Z","msg":"其實depends on 好多factors<br />\n包括你有無同當地人拍拖 一齊同居每晚親密交流 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9680b242340c6a9896a92bb6dff362fa0f918a","tid":479101,"uid":66045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T18:01:43.000Z","msg":"識得好多由細係香港大既外國人大部分都係識聽<br />\n但唔多識講<br />\n所以我諗家庭因素都幾重要"},{"pid":"6146b0c124536c38b61a4a3bf006d3ff57b75e7c","tid":479101,"uid":69779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T21:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e5/Kenneth_L._Pike.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fe%2Fe5%2FKenneth_L._Pike.jpg&h=b06fb470&s={SIZE}\" />：有何難哉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a917a2a386f3b55eb7d28f75b6c143e89d1e1164","tid":479101,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:16:55.000Z","msg":"CIA話1000個鐘頭已經夠秒殺多數既語言（for English speakers learning most Indo-European languages)"},{"pid":"e2f740faa5d1b3a7a8f91b51bbc1d07dd18d4a6b","tid":479101,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T02:19:44.000Z","msg":"會識講，但如果真係完全無教育既話<br />\n好大機會係文盲"}]}